Qatar Begins Work on Link to Bahrain, Al-Sharq Reports

-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 
2011-02-21T07:56:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/qatar-begins-work-on-link-to-bahrain-al-sharq-reports.html
Qatar began preparatory work for the
construction of a 40 kilometer link to the island of  Bahrain ,
 Al-Sharq reported , without saying how the information was
obtained.  Work has started on the area within Qatar where the first
concrete will be laid, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Robert Tuttle in Doha at 
 rtuttle@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss on   sev@bloomberg.net  